من آمده آم  ManAamade-am is an Afghani song and was  sung by Iranian singer Googosh,
This song was written and composed by an Afghan singer, composer, musician   Ustad Dzeland. He gave the song to Googoosh as gift, while she was in Afghanistan for performing a concert in early 1970s. Mr.Dzeland's two daughters Shahla and Suhailah Dzeland are  both  singers. Unfortunately Gogoosh or Iranian State TV failed to mentioned the song was a gift to them.
